# WhatsApp / Surge Rule Set
# 适用于 Surge RULE-SET
# 建议策略：Proxy / DIRECT 按需在 Surge 配置中指定

DOMAIN-SUFFIX,whatsapp.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,whatsapp.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,wa.me
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,whatsappbrand.com

# WhatsApp 常见媒体 / CDN / 连接域名
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cdn.whatsapp.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mmg.whatsapp.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pps.whatsapp.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,g.whatsapp.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,v.whatsapp.net

# 兜底关键词，避免漏掉动态子域名
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,whatsapp
